Header for handling UNIX terminal colors
C and C++ compatible

Copyright (C) 2010 Romain Porte
This header is under GPL ( for more info see the COPYING file )
     
=======
 USAGE
=======

 C :

printf("%sGreen%s\n", TC_Green, TC_Default);

 C++ :

std::cout << TC_Green << "Green" << TC_Default << std::endl;
